data.description: Welcome to your dream home in the heart of Easley! This beautifully maintained 3-bedroom, 2-bathroom residence offers a perfect blend of comfort, style, and modern amenities.  As you step inside, you'll be greeted by the warmth of the dining and living room with rich dark wood floors. The recently updated kitchen featuring stunning granite countertops and all-new appliances is right off of the dining room. The refrigerator is graciously included, ensuring a seamless transition into your new culinary haven.   Upstairs, a versatile bonus room awaits your creative touch—perfect for a home office, playroom, or additional guest space. The possibilities are endless!  The exterior boasts a screened porch, offering a serene retreat for relaxation or entertaining guests. Two additional deck areas provide the ideal setting for al fresco dining or enjoying the Carolina sunshine. With a sprawling .52-acre lot, there's plenty of room for outdoor activities and gardening.    Convenience is key, and this property delivers. Situated in a prime location, you'll find yourself just moments away from shopping destinations, ensuring that your daily errands are a breeze. Close proximity to Hunt Meadows Elementary and Wren Middle School
